{"type": "article", "id": 12931, "title": "日式自挂邮箱", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-03T07:40:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606061405190HUTqYKArPh9ODQ4.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t东京 S&amp;O 设计工作室的设计师 Hisakazu Shimizu 最近推出了一个叫做 “Fumi” 的自挂邮箱系列，“uri”，“kasumi” 和 “matsu” 是三款上下抽拉样式设计，而 “ki” 和 “kaze” 则是两款横向推拉样式设计。邮箱的图案均采取清新的日和风格，不管是传统的院落，还是现代化的装饰风格，都可以找到适合的邮箱。这是<a href=\"http://sandodesign.com/\" target=\"_blank\">工作室的主页</a>，对日式风格感兴趣的话，不妨进来看看。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140617Mkf8slp9CyzTiO7S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70925926\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140617KHwd9kIsR7Nt0jom.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.26944444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016072614061831fcNnykEBwtAgSX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.86388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016072614061825GzVy3svxA7mLaW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.26203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261406192LHDTitPpw3cGB9u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.26203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140619jNhGuZLedbBw4cz7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140620MT2lVRr1UmzvaefE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.26203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}